commitResults.messageTitle: Change person card to list information horizontally.
commitResults.messageBody:
Initially, details will be listed vertically, with name and then phone, email and availability below

However, this wasted the large horizontal space present on computers

Lets list the details in horizontal columns so that it is easier to read

Previously, app had a grey colour scheme

This was pretty boring for users

Lets mke our colour scheme more colorful sousers enjoy using our app

commitResults.messageTitle: Fix the arrangement of the volunteer details
commitResults.messageBody:
Previously, the placement of email and address was dependent on the length of phone (fixed distance from phone)

This made the information disorganised if phone had different length

Lets put details in columns so it is more organised

commitResults.messageTitle: Change DG to reflect proposed Copy Command
commitResults.messageBody:
Copy command allows us to copy all emails of a filtered list to have easier communication

Previously, the DG did not include the details of this command

Lets update the DG so it documents all commands
Add Assignment Feature

Changed the execute(undo) label in a sequence diagram

Diagram was for the copy command, so executing undo was the wrong label

Lets make sure our labels are correct

commitResults.messageTitle: Add feature to extract emails from Filtered List
commitResults.messageBody:
Using the copy command, we can extract all emails in a comma-seperated format

Previously we were unable to obtain the contact details in a single command

Lets make it easier to copy all contact details and contact our volunteers

Allow the filtered list of emails to be copied to the clipboard

Previously, the filtered list of emails was only printed to the command line

Lets copy it to to the clipboard so it can be pasted easily

Add CopyCommandTest

Previously, had no testcases to ensure that CopyCommand was working properly

Lets test all functionality

Remove unused methods and reorder import statements

Previously, there were some issues that were detected by checker

Lets make sure our code abides by checkstyles
